[{"Name":"Scott Vandekerckhove","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocII1RAmhnxUdBsrE0YJ6tNZQPtr2lZ9dpilxEVvMI5PMnD1Lm4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabrielle provided me with nothing but the very best service for nearly six years.  She was always super kind, talkative, and expertly professional.  Anyone looking for waxing or eyebrow treatment will be well taken care of under her watch.  A+ all the way and I'd recommend her to literally everyone I could.

@Gabrielle, thanks for everything during my time here in Dallas and all the best in your life and career!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jasmine George","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2B-vdMdxP9CmGym0zSV3e-3gbY9mDW6zV-woE0VihNTubEG4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabrielle has such a great friendly personality! My experience was amazing! Her suite is so fun and cutsey! She’s so fast and gets everything! I mean EVERY HAIR OFF! LOL I absolutely love someone that doesn’t delay with the snatches. That’s honestly what keeps me coming back! You’ll be done before you even know! Because ladies..IDC what no one says waxing is painful every time but I’m always amazed with the smooth results! Please BOOK with her!!! You won’t regret it! XOXO","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blair Coble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIX-SPqYPvrm4_yADguTD-EA94A7Oxt3vtKsLJLgc6l-9bJJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had my first appointment with Gabrielle and she was absolutely phenomenal! Her space is so welcoming, clean, and fun—it immediately put me at ease. Gabriella made me feel incredibly comfortable and cared for from start to finish. She’s thorough, personable, and extremely professional. This was hands down the most painless waxing experience I’ve ever had, and the results were amazing. I’m definitely coming back and would highly recommend her to anyone looking for a great waxing experience. She’s a gem!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ellie Quilca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQ9hqaZrIqSRGxQOrHEKMVT0QudaDk7QEoQ4d0i5Kra2ec6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m beyond happy with my hair! Gab nailed the color perfectly and made sure everything looked flawless. Super friendly, professional, and talented! 10/10 experience and definitely my go-to from now on!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristen Lowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Cce1YJ91uNDopC3ZsQMqJCrskbkJpIHz3vHT3A2VlobDDVT_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Gabby for 2 years now and she is THE BEST! She does the best Brazilian and always makes sure to take her time to make me look and feel great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Howard Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfY36odcN-EEe30c82Hs71OapCy2DZHFJvUxwyFOMhzIxZELFK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabrielle was extremely friendly and professional. She spent time with me making me feel important and that she would definitely take care of my needs. After our visit making sure that she would meet all of my needs. She made the time and treatments made me feel like royalty. Her personality and caring ways have made me an ongoing schedule for taking care of myself.
I refer my (especially women friends for her with her great treatments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samar Wales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV21jH09m5cL4s-kGKoQvqFCBpHTb2mtRC9H-BRA7Vc2edIPYYAoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Gabrielle for my waxing services for years, and she’s simply the best! She has a gentle touch and uses high-quality wax products, which makes all the difference. Gabrielle creates a comfortable environment while maintaining the utmost professionalism. I wouldn’t trust anyone else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesaias Benitez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdTEgLWMqBqklSGOPDCiWlMumWR_eEPCLuzvUL4EUxnhTu_Qn3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s always great to go visit Gabriella ! She always does an amazing job on my brows exactly how I want them done ! This place is chill and welcoming!  She always takes her time is super professional and always leaves them looking 🔥🔥🔥 Definitely recommend and will be trying out other services too!","Images":null,"When":""}]
